{
  "2388990": {
    "name": "ShadowKitty: Thief by Night",
    "steam_appid": 2388990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>白天是高中生，晚上是小偷！</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/5d27155f104547b8863ce770d98fc710.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=347 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/8c4b6a254a64aca01866b57232e4c3ab.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=166 /></span><br><br><strong>ShadowKitty：夜贼</strong> 讲述了一位十几岁的猫女从罪犯手中偷回被盗艺术品并将其全部带回博物馆的冒险故事。<br><br>该游戏是一款有趣的 <strong>2D 动作平台游戏</strong>，其灵感源自 <strong>Megaman X</strong>、<strong>Spelunky</strong>、<strong>Ducktales Remastered</strong> 和 <strong>CupHead</strong>，同时也受到复古卡通节目的启发，例如<strong>蝙蝠侠：动画系列</strong>、<strong>DuckTales</strong>、<strong>TMNT - 忍者神龟</strong>、<strong>X 战警</strong> 和<strong>黑翼鸭</strong>。游戏中也有一些<strong>动漫</strong>的影响。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/b53f661f4bd5013988f15de542de5a77.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br><i>- 由于游戏仍在开发中，因此开发时间可能比计划的时间更长 -</i><br><i>- 目前没有游戏视频，我将在今年晚些时候发布 -</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/60a6978bc394c3c369b92d9f2755f851.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=350 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>❖ 游戏特色❖</strong></h2><br><br>· 2D 动作平台游戏<br>· 程序级别<br>· <strong>1 名玩家</strong>（故事模式）<br>· 语言：<strong>英语</strong><br>· 阶段：13<br>· 卡通风格/动画暴力<br>· 视觉小说故事片段<br>· 击败游戏后解锁她的对手 <strong>Arséne Mask</strong><br>· 引擎：Unity<br>· 发布日期：待定<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/a283c90269fd68afa9e89b5910c2dd51.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=287 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>❖ 游戏玩法❖</strong></h2><br><br>《Shadowkitty》将是一款快节奏的动作平台游戏，您必须在每个阶段中搜索被盗艺术，并在每个阶段结束时击败 <strong>Boss</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/b706c688d72d4d510209f2a28cdccda5.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=262 /></span><br><br>ShadowKitty 可以用她的爪子进行<strong>连击</strong>或使用非致命武器（<strong>软糖枪</strong>、<strong>回旋镖</strong>和<strong>烟雾弹</strong>）对抗她的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/03f4403d7e0a9622f3daf7e5f128e77b.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>如果您在每个常规阶段收集<strong>秘密艺术品</strong>，您就可以<strong>解锁</strong>一个<strong>秘密老板</strong>，但不用担心，您可以<strong>重播</strong>，我的意思是随时再次<strong>“重演”</strong>每个阶段，但由于阶段的布局都是<strong>程序性</strong>，因此每次播放时布局总是会改变游戏或进入/重新开始一个阶段。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/6265f25db964380aacc21858bd9e6b95.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=347 /></span><br><br>阶段中有一些<strong>谜题</strong>，但没有什么真正复杂的，比如躲避激光、寻找钥匙、躲避探照灯或按下终端中的按钮在有限的时间内解锁门。<br><br>游戏中还有一些<strong>视觉小说</strong>故事片段（但您可以跳过所有过场动画）。<br>被击败的<strong>Boss</strong>将在游戏的最后阶段再次出现<strong>重新战斗</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/9313c0b953440cd24d7712418ad9bfc7.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=250 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>❖ 核心特性❖</strong></h2><br><br>• 探索（程序级别）<br>• 时限<br>• 解决难题<br>• 与敌人战斗<br>• 收集艺术品<br>• 击败舞台老大<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/128bc3126d665f36ff64f58f46b7f05e.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=250 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>❖ 游戏模式 ❖</strong></h2><br><br>该游戏计划有几种游戏模式：<br><br>• 故事模式<br>• 挑战<br>• Boss 冲刺<br>• 生存<br>• 画廊<br>• 排行榜<br><br>某些游戏模式可能有一些难度选项：<strong>简单</strong>、<strong>正常</strong>、<strong>困难</strong>或<strong>狂热</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/7155aa2c76572c3466b0523e9a5e3367.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>❖ 预期年龄评级 ❖</strong></h2><br><br>ShadowKitty 的目标是 <strong>ESRB +10</strong>、<strong>PEGI 12</strong> 和 <strong>CERO B</strong> 评级。<br>它将包含<strong>卡通暴力</strong>和一些轻微的<strong>温和语言</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/0db703e0c180b74fc1553f44faaa5424.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=250 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>❖ 语言 ❖</strong></h2><br><br>游戏的主要语言为<strong>英语</strong>，可选择<strong>葡萄牙语BR</strong>字幕。如果游戏获得足够的翻译资金，我们计划添加<strong>更多语言</strong>。<br><br>计划的语言（仅限字幕和菜单）可能包括：<strong>西班牙语</strong>、<strong>德语</strong>、<strong>意大利语</strong>、<strong>法语</strong>、<strong>简体中文</strong>、<strong>日语</strong>、<strong>韩语</strong>、<strong>泰语</strong>和<strong>阿拉伯语</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/bb351483e6bbaea2fe6438953d318548.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=260 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>❖ 发展❖</strong></h2><br><br>该游戏的所有动画均使用<strong>手绘精灵</strong>。<br>ShadowKitty：夜贼目前处于<strong>原型</strong>阶段。<br>稍后将提供游戏的简短<strong>演示</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/55d23a772019ee4685a216ef57b50857.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=368 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>❖ 字符❖</strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/4bce5648c252fbee24b69e110b346f17.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=299 /></span><br><br>了解游戏的主角和所有 Boss：<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/6b69275374d131132e32cd28bd57da58.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦ ShadowKitty (Alyssia KittyField)</strong><br>一名高中生试图从博物馆找回所有被盗的艺术品。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/e35b8f0197ed506316c0834678372bb0.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦ 阿尔塞纳面具（未知）</strong><br>ShadowKitty的对手。来自海外的神秘小偷，戴着高科技面具。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/7684df529c212083255bb7d479d2a1c5.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦ 忍者猫英二（石川英二）</strong><br>作为一个古老忍者家族的继承人，他被操纵去犯罪。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/e0626b94b0d6861d74e35a4467de4adc.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦ 蜂王安妮特 (Annette Pantalonia)</strong><br>一只危险的蜂王和数百名蜂仆。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/5de38492f29f50874ee73a037da98b25.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦ 大白牙 (Paollo Whitefang)</strong><br>托尼·蒙蒂格的右手。他还指挥该组织的追随者。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/5e215f678cdce5671eaa0613db8b2864.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦ Mei Kitty (美龄冠玉)</strong><br>强大的亚洲猫科动物。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/bffa7c8369b17f4fd4d35aa376af3c8e.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦朋克狼（鲁尔·阿什纳德）</strong><br>一位拥有令人震惊的技巧的吉他手。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/d26fee170b4fcf9a6cebd671e1f69e8d.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦ Chimp Lee（闹国王李）</strong><br>一位武术爱好者。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/d1a6a4349e743a83ddedcbc69de219db.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦电视头</strong><br>一只疯狂的猫在城市里经营着一家危险的电视台。没有人知道他实际上是机器人、半机械人还是其他什么东西。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/829b8ac6ababb6c8f2840abbeb9153f4.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦ 女巫凯蒂 (Selina Le Rouge)</strong><br>来自猫科女巫血统的强大青少年女巫。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/252775eac110e93e1d3021d8b2021611.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦ 莉迪亚·暗兔 (Lydia de Caligari)</strong><br>来自海外的强力兔子魔法师。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/f856afb107c8ef2cab06b503c1bccd73.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦伯爵夫人血石（奥尔德里德血石）</strong><br>一位孤独的歌手被她的音乐经纪人欺骗而犯罪。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/4a177d80da4dcbf833a8609ceca7c592.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦ 弗洛拉·阿尔劳恩</strong><br>歌剧演员，托尼·蒙蒂格的养女。她统治着这座城市的赌场。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/8c91973f7f2d34ed49e460f3dc204965.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦ 托尼·蒙蒂格</strong><br>通过犯罪组织统治城市的黑帮。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/a00f01204681243c9d761ba732d78aae.avif?t=1734708474\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><strong>✦死亡（秘密老板）</strong><br>她不是“真正的死亡”，她实际上来自噩梦。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/691bf7181019e7a541b1a11aa8e95787.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=125 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>❖ 关于开发商 ❖</strong></h2><br><br><strong>StarQuarius Studio</strong> 是一家位于巴西<strong>圣保罗</strong>的单人游戏工作室。<br>我们唯一的使命是利用现代技术创造创新且有趣的优质 <strong>2D 游戏</strong>，但始终植根于古老的经典游戏。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/3296c56d7514d707a93d7145e6f60237.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>► 随着游戏的制作，请继续关注更多更新，喵！</strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/4e75f85f587818223bf413f067193249.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/fef68384e3b2ac034c4c975637dc9e13.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=124 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/04e35a64701ca9cfe56dc010efa83cdc.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=110 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388990/extras/74d52d89c5d46bef18315c22f8ebd5a7.avif?t=1734708474\" width=616 height=96 /></span>",
